    • addArchitecture

      public static void addArchitecture(Architecture architecture) throws Street.InvalidPositionException, Street.PositionOccupiedException, Street.NotEnoughSpaceException
      Adds given architecture to street of the program. User is needed to enter a side of the street for architecture to be added on.
      Parameters:
      architecture - Architecture to be built/added to the street
      Throws:
      Street.InvalidPositionException - When position of the architecture is outside the street
      Street.PositionOccupiedException - When another architecture is in the way
      Street.NotEnoughSpaceException - When architecture doesn't fit in the street
